<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "3A">
<servcat sctnbr = "03" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "1">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B3116009" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" page = "2" supplyoff = "1">
<title>
Drive Intermediate Shaft Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B3116005">Drive Intermediate Shaft Assembly Removal and Installation:Front</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B3116009001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove circlip (1) from drive intermediate shaft.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311020.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.317mm" ver = "02" gw = "165" gh = "118"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using hydraulic press (1), remove drive intermediate shaft (2) with dust shield (3) from intermediate shaft bearing (4).
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
If shaft is pushed with base (5) put just under dust shield, dust shield will interfere with base and dust shield can damage.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Do not put base of hydraulic press just under dust shield.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311018.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.303mm" ver = "02" gw = "118" gh = "132"/>
</figure>
</attention2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311021.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.200mm" ver = "02" gw = "123" gh = "111"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove dust seal(s) (1) from intermediate shaft bearing support using special tool.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
For M/T model, dust seals are on both sides.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
For A/T model, dust seal is on drive shaft side only.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A103">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-50121">
09913–50121
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311003.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "54.730mm" ver = "01" gw = "188" gh = "139"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove snap ring (1) using snap ring pliers (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I6RS0B310006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.434mm" ver = "03" gw = "90" gh = "123"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using hydraulic press (2) and special tool, remove intermediate shaft bearing from intermediate shaft bearing support (1) by pushing the bearing from transaxle side.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A104">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-75810">
09913–75810
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.852mm" ver = "01" gw = "178" gh = "125"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove deflector (1) and/or dust shield from intermediate shaft using flat-bladed screwdriver or the like, if necessary.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.239mm" ver = "01" gw = "156" gh = "132"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B3116009002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install new deflector (1) onto drive intermediate shaft, if removed, by tapping flat-surface of deflector indicated by arrow in figure, along the circle little by little and using flat-end rod covered with cloth (2) to protect deflector from damage.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Denting or scratching the oil seal contact surface of drive intermediate shaft will oil leakage.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Do not damage the contact surface when installing the deflector.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Incomplete installation of the deflector will damage the oil seal and result in oil leakage.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Confirm the deflector end (3) contacts with the shoulder (4) of the shaft evenly.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311019.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "78.493mm" ver = "01" gw = "208" gh = "206"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
For A/T model, install new dust shield (1) to drive intermediate shaft using special tool, if removed.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A105">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09927-66010">
09927–66010
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311011.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "46.687mm" ver = "02" gw = "132" gh = "116"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using hydraulic press (2) and special tools, install new intermediate shaft bearing to intermediate shaft bearing support (1) by pushing the bearing from drive shaft side.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A106">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-75520">
09913–75520
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A107">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09924-74510">
09924–74510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A108">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09944-68510">
09944–68510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<title>
M/T model
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311012.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.336mm" ver = "01" gw = "171" gh = "123"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<title>
A/T model
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.334mm" ver = "01" gw = "173" gh = "109"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install new snap ring (1) in groove (2) of intermediate shaft bearing support.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311011.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "79.321mm" ver = "01" gw = "150" gh = "208"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
For M/T model, apply grease (2 – 3 g) to seal lip of new dust seal on transaxle side and space on bearing as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<materials>
<materialitem name = "SUZUKI Super Grease A" id = "M3A101" uid = "1126491901">
<m-part>
“A”
</m-part>
<m-desc>
Grease
</m-desc>
<m-number>
99000–25011
</m-number>
<m-name>
SUZUKI Super Grease A
</m-name>
</materialitem>
</materials>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311012.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.205mm" ver = "02" gw = "79" gh = "106"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
For M/T model, install new dust seal (1) to specified position on transaxle side of intermediate shaft bearing support in specified direction shown in figure using special tool.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A109">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-15410">
09925–15410
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<spec>
<title>
Distance
</title>
<ptxt>
“a”: 6 – 7 mm (0.24 – 0.28 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311014.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "62.312mm" ver = "01" gw = "101" gh = "160"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply grease (2 – 3 g) to seal lip of new dust seal on drive shaft side and space on bearing as shown in figures.
</ptxt>
<materials>
<materialitem name = "SUZUKI Super Grease A" id = "M3A102" uid = "1126491901">
<m-part>
“A”
</m-part>
<m-desc>
Grease
</m-desc>
<m-number>
99000–25011
</m-number>
<m-name>
SUZUKI Super Grease A
</m-name>
</materialitem>
</materials>
<figure>
<title>
M/T model
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311015.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "41.797mm" ver = "03" gw = "158" gh = "102"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<title>
A/T model
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311016.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "42.268mm" ver = "03" gw = "147" gh = "103"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install new dust seal (1) to the specified position on drive shaft side of intermediate shaft bearing support in specified direction shown in figure using special tools.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A110">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09926-27610">
09926–27610
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A111">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09924-74510">
09924–74510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A112">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-17910">
09925–17910
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<spec>
<title>
Distance
</title>
<ptxt>
M/T model:
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
“a”: 0.5 – 1.5 mm (0.02 – 0.05 in.)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
A/T model:
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
“a”: 0.5 – 2.5 mm (0.02 – 0.09 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<title>
M/T model
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311015.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "72.532mm" ver = "01" gw = "157" gh = "189"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<title>
A/T model
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311016.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "64.919mm" ver = "02" gw = "120" gh = "168"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Press-fit drive intermediate shaft (2) into inner race (1) of intermediate shaft bearing from transaxle side using hydraulic press (3) and special tool.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A113">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-84510">
09913–84510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B311017.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "83.290mm" ver = "01" gw = "211" gh = "220"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install new circlip (1) to intermediate shaft.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60A311020.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.317mm" ver = "02" gw = "165" gh = "118"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
